## Known Issues / Notes
- WSL conf syntax: no leading spaces in /etc/wsl.conf (caused parse error)
- apt lock conflicts: parallel apt installs cause lock contention, run sequentially
- nvidia-smi not in default PATH, needs /usr/lib/wsl/lib in PATH
- Ollama needs to be started manually after WSL restart (add to wsl.conf boot command)
